      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Good things are happening! America’s largest labor union announced an effort this week to organize Amazon warehouses across the country, while the mammoth retailer is also about to face new regulatory scrutiny. Also, the Democratic Socialists of America are suing the private company that profits from Chicago’s parking meters, while the former president of the National Rifle Association is tricked into a stunt that perfectly illustrates the impact of the gun industry’s loathsome lobbying efforts.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
